&lt;h3&gt;Setup: The Happy Path (~30 min)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. SonarCloud&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;small&gt;Import your project via "Analyze new project" (don't create manually). Disable Automatic Analysis. Generate a &lt;b&gt;Project Analysis Token&lt;/b&gt; (not a user token ‚Äî this matters, see Challenge #3).&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. GitHub PAT (Fine-grained)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

