‚ú® Core Bots &amp;amp; Features
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Copy Trading Bot&lt;/strong&gt; (Rust)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Automatically mirror trades from top/winning Polymarket wallets&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
‚Üí Multi-trader support (follow several at once)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
