&lt;h3&gt;


Why Rust? ‚ö°
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blazing fast execution (critical for arbitrage &amp;amp; low-latency copy-trading)
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Memory safety ‚Üí fewer bugs in financial code
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;~97% Rust codebase ‚Üí clean, performant, and modern&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


Quick Start (Simulator ‚Äì zero risk)
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Try the &lt;strong&gt;demo simulator Telegram bot&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Üí &lt;a href="https://t.me/poly_copy_tg_bot" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://t.me/poly_copy_tg_bot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
(educational version ‚Äì shows copy-trading flows safely)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
