&lt;span class="p"&gt;))}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;The carousel view maps over the same array and renders full-width slides:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

