‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;High performance&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Comparable to C/C++&lt;br&gt;
‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;Modern features&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Pattern matching, algebraic types&lt;br&gt;
‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;Growing community&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Active development&lt;br&gt;
‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;High demand&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Top salaries ($150K-$300K+ in US)&lt;br&gt;
‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;No data races&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Compiler prevents them&lt;br&gt;
‚úÖ &lt;strong&gt;Speed + Safety + Stability&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Three elements of 2026 system programming&lt;/p&gt;

