‚ùå &lt;strong&gt;Compilation time&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Can be lengthy&lt;br&gt;
‚ùå &lt;strong&gt;Fewer entry-level jobs&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Experience required&lt;br&gt;
‚ùå &lt;strong&gt;Borrow checker&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Conceptually challenging&lt;br&gt;
‚ùå &lt;strong&gt;Fewer libraries&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Than more mature languages&lt;/p&gt;

