Final Recommendations
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


For Absolute Beginners
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Start with Python or JavaScript&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Most entry-level job openings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Master fundamental concepts&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Algorithms, data structures, OOP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Build a portfolio&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî 3-5 pet projects to demonstrate skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Don't search for the perfect language&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Programming principles transfer between languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


For Career Changers
