&lt;strong&gt;Research your local market&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Jobs vary geographically&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Consider enterprise languages&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Java, C# for stability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Use online courses&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Flexible learning without leaving your job&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

