&lt;h3&gt;


3. Time Travel / History Middleware
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Store history for debugging and time-travel:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
