&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros:&lt;/strong&gt; Built-in, no dependencies&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Cons:&lt;/strong&gt; Causes unnecessary re-renders, verbose, provider hell with multiple contexts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;


2. Redux
