&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros:&lt;/strong&gt; Predictable, powerful, large ecosystem&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Cons:&lt;/strong&gt; Lots of boilerplate, steep learning curve, large bundle size (~6KB)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;


3. Zustand
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A modern, lightweight alternative:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

